602
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:14,130
I can't hold onto it?

603
00:31:16,120 --> 00:31:18,760
I can't really explain it either,

604
00:31:18,760 --> 00:31:21,040
what love truly is.

605
00:31:21,280 --> 00:31:22,840
Because everyone understands love

606
00:31:22,840 --> 00:31:23,840
differently.

