00:31:24,440 --> 00:31:25,720
But as someone who's been

608
00:31:25,720 --> 00:31:27,580
hanging around for over 40 years,

609
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,360
my advice to you is,

610
00:31:29,800 --> 00:31:33,080
when you can't hold onto love, hold onto your child.

611
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:37,440
Are you ready to respond to the lawsuit? It's your call.

612
00:31:37,440 --> 00:31:40,120
Of course. I must get my child back.

613
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:44,440
I'll arrange a lawyer for you tomorrow.

614
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:45,880
Old fox.

615
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:51,680
Thanks.

616
00:32:01,360 --> 00:32:03,000
Everyone, Mr. Qin is here.

617
00:32:04,640 --> 00:32:05,500
Hello, Mr. Qin.

618
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,360
Mr. Qin.

619
00:32:07,520 --> 00:32:09,760
These are all elite professionals in our field.

620
00:32:09,760 --> 00:32:11,320
Even on a national level,

621
00:32:11,320 --> 00:32:13,640
they are among the top lawyers in the country.

622
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:15,360
I've put in a lot of effort,

