658
00:33:44,760 --> 00:33:46,420
Qin Gang is behind this again.

659
00:33:48,000 --> 00:33:49,160
I swear, Wan Xinxin.

660
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:50,600
I called one firm after another

661
00:33:50,600 --> 00:33:51,860
