685
00:34:48,920 --> 00:34:50,440
This case is extremely important to us.

686
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:52,040
We're very anxious about it.

687
00:34:52,199 --> 00:34:53,480
I just want to ask you,

688
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:55,600
what are our chances of winning?

689
00:34:55,800 --> 00:34:57,530
I've reviewed your documents.

690
00:34:58,080 --> 00:35:00,210
I think there's still hope of winning.

691
00:35:00,880 --> 00:35:04,080
The child is young and still nursing.

692
00:35:05,160 --> 00:35:06,560
This works in your favor.

693
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:09,640
But to win this case,

694
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:11,840
