695
00:35:12,600 --> 00:35:13,440
What problem?

696
00:35:13,840 --> 00:35:15,520
You currently don't have a job.

697
00:35:15,520 --> 00:35:16,850
This indicates that you

698
00:35:16,960 --> 00:35:19,120
don't have the ability to raise a child.

699
00:35:19,120 --> 00:35:20,520
To win this case,

700
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:22,480
you need to quickly find

701
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:24,120
a job with decent income.

702
00:35:40,240 --> 00:35:40,920
Xinxin.

703
00:35:46,480 --> 00:35:48,560
I've summarized some options for you.

704
00:35:48,560 --> 00:35:50,160
Take a look at this one first.

705
00:35:50,560 --> 00:35:52,020
The base salary is too low.

706
00:35:53,000 --> 00:35:54,130
This one seems fine.

707
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:56,880
I need to find a high-paying job.

708
00:35:57,200 --> 00:35:58,520
I absolutely cannot let Qin Gang and others

709
00:35:58,520 --> 00:36:00,120
find any excuse to attack me.

710
00:36:01,240 --> 00:36:03,240
Alright. What about this one?

711
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:08,520
This one looks promising.

712
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:09,920
Let's go with this one then.

713
00:36:09,920 --> 00:36:10,720
I'll contact them.

714
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:11,120
Good.

715
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:15,200
182.

716
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:25,420
Do you have any other additional requirements?

717
00:36:25,720 --> 00:36:26,520
No.

718
00:36:27,040 --> 00:36:28,240
Such a good attitude.

719
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:32,050
As they say nowadays, attitude determines everything.

720
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,600
Your resume is excellent.

721
00:36:35,160 --> 00:36:37,360
And I've heard about

722
00:36:37,720 --> 00:36:39,450
many of your previous designs.

723
00:36:39,680 --> 00:36:42,400
So, you can start working here next week.

724
00:36:43,240 --> 00:36:44,000
Really?

725
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:44,480
Really.

726
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:46,400
Thank you, Manager Yang.

727
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:48,160
