729
00:36:49,720 --> 00:36:50,440
Good.

730
00:36:50,560 --> 00:36:52,160
Okay, I'll be going now.

731
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:52,800
Goodbye.

732
00:36:52,800 --> 00:36:53,640
Okay, goodbye.

733
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:54,320
Goodbye.

734
00:36:54,720 --> 00:36:55,440
See you next week.

735
00:36:55,440 --> 00:36:56,300
Okay, goodbye.

736
00:37:05,600 --> 00:37:06,400
Mr. Yang

737
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,520
Editor Liu

738
00:37:07,520 --> 00:37:09,380
Long time no see. Please sit down.

739
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:11,640
Been quite busy lately.

740
00:37:11,640 --> 00:37:13,400
Not bad. You're still so beautiful.

741
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:14,840
