743
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:20,760
That person just now.

744
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:22,620
It's her. You know each other?

745
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:25,760
Not really.

746
00:37:26,560 --> 00:37:29,000
