783
00:39:22,080 --> 00:39:23,280
Don't follow me.

784
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:26,570
Do you feel really frustrated inside?

785
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:28,600
Yes.

786
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:35,500
Then I'll take you somewhere.

787
00:39:55,520 --> 00:39:56,680
I got fired again.

788
00:40:00,440 --> 00:40:02,760
I ran into Liu Wei when I went out today.

789
00:40:03,640 --> 00:40:05,760
She's up to something again, isn't she?

790
00:40:05,760 --> 00:40:07,960
What exactly do they want?

791
00:40:09,120 --> 00:40:10,560
I just want my baby boy.

792
00:40:10,760 --> 00:40:12,240
Is that wrong?

793
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:16,760
They stop me when I try to find a lawyer.

794
00:40:17,040 --> 00:40:19,400
They even prevent me from finding a job.

795
00:40:19,520 --> 00:40:22,120
They just want to take my baby away, don't they?

796
00:40:22,480 --> 00:40:23,480
But my baby is still so little.

797
00:40:23,480 --> 00:40:25,140
He needs his mother right now.

798
00:40:26,440 --> 00:40:29,040
I absolutely cannot let them take my baby away.

799
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:30,520
I, Wan Xinxin,

800
00:40:30,520 --> 00:40:32,480
no matter how much I suffer or how unfairly I'm treated,

801
00:40:32,480 --> 00:40:34,640
I will never let them take my baby away.

802
00:40:36,960 --> 00:40:39,160
I'm already backed into a corner by them

803
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:41,040
with no way out.

804
00:41:00,600 --> 00:41:01,440
Wan Xinxin.

805
00:41:02,840 --> 00:41:03,320
Do you know

806
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:04,880
why I brought you here?

807
00:41:05,080 --> 00:41:07,200
Because I've faced many difficulties in my life too,

808
00:41:07,200 --> 00:41:08,600
problems I couldn't solve on my own.

809
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,840
Sometimes I feel like I'm about to explode,

810
00:41:10,840 --> 00:41:11,640
so I come here.

811
00:41:11,960 --> 00:41:12,800
I need to vent too.

812
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:13,730
I need conflict.

813
00:41:20,480 --> 00:41:22,880
I thought shouting would be enough to let it all out.

814
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:23,800
