00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:45,250
But you're different, Wan Xinxin.

823
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:46,120
You know what?

824
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:48,440
You're the first girl

825
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:51,200
