826
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:53,900
Because I think you're special, Wan Xinxin.

827
00:41:54,720 --> 00:41:55,560
Who are you?

828
00:41:55,680 --> 00:41:58,480
You're someone who can't be steamed or boiled,

829
00:41:58,480 --> 00:42:01,320
